<h2><%= namespace_cost.namespace %></h2>

<p>
These are costs as reported by <a href="https://infracost.io">infracost</a>.
Only AWS resources belonging to the namespace are included (i.e. shared resources
including cluster running and support costs are not included), and only where
infracost reports on resources of that type (see their list of
<a href="https://www.infracost.io/docs/supported_resources">supported resources</a>).
</p>

<table class="table table-striped">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Resource</th>
      <th>Monthly Cost ($)</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <% namespace_cost.resources.each do |resource| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= resource.fetch(:name) %></td>
        <td class="text-right"><%= commify resource.fetch(:monthly_cost) %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
  <tfoot>
    <tr>
      <th>Total</th>
      <th class="text-right"><%= commify namespace_cost.total %></th>
    </tr>
  </tfoot>
</table>
